Failure Modes (Coil Lens)

* Too much Rabbit → chaos, no direction
* Too much Digger → paralysis (too many options)
* Too much Listener → overthinking, delay
* Too much Runner → sprinting into traps

Balance = fluid switching, not fixed identity.

